Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constra...averaging_mode(25.10)  timing_constra...averaging_mode(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_update_io_latency_averaging_mode

Syntax
       timing_constraint_update_io_latency_averaging_mode

       {rise_fall | rise_only}

       Default : rise_fall

       Controls  the  analysis to update IO latency for both rise and fall, or
       for rise only. You can set one of the options - rise_fall, rise_only.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

